{"tid":1748647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再有英國大學SU出聲譴責香港警暴","createTime":"2019-11-23T18:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T01:15:08.000Z","uid":325795,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3e195fe1b80fe9fb9b30f06ce5de241fe5635b","tid":1748647,"uid":325795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:56:16.000Z","msg":"英國2020 Guardian University Guide僅次於劍橋大學、排名第二嘅聖安德魯大學University of St. Andrews （即係威廉王子讀嗰間，下稱UStA) 學生會於11月19日全數通過對香港警方濫暴作出譴責並全力支援為香港示威者發聲嘅學生。(UStA)於11月20日對於理大事件發出聲明，強烈譴責香港政府對民主及言論自由嘅嚴重踐踏。聲明中亦譴責香港警方濫用暴力對待學生，並全力支援因為反送中運動發聲而受欺凌嘅學生。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<br />\nStatement on the Police Brutality in Chinese University of Hong Kong and Hong Kong Polytechnic University:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The University of St Andrew's Students Association totally and unreservedly condemns the attack on democracy, free speech, and students that took place in Hong Kong last week. Closer to home, and no less importantly, it condemns the bullying and targeted harassment of Hong Kong students who have spoken out about the protests. Any instances of bullying should be reported to the University discipline officer (discipline@)&quot;<br />\n<br />\n學生會全體通過：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/113100653481661/posts/116140799844313?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F113100653481661%2Fposts%2F116140799844313%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=5623c773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/113100653481661/posts/116140799844313?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n聲明: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1397338077205269/posts/2413969288875471?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1397338077205269%2Fposts%2F2413969288875471%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=8fe11053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1397338077205269/posts/2413969288875471?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n據悉早前劍橋同牛津學生會都出咗譴責聲明，即係英國頭三間己經出咗聲譴責警暴同支持呢場運動，國際戰線繼續做嘢。"},{"pid":"a75c3466745c3703984d6f633533738e0d8bce2f","tid":1748647,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:57:01.000Z","msg":"有撚用？"},{"pid":"c5e6f1242dc3ea6945e31f0486db30a7bc03f7c4","tid":1748647,"uid":78651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"有錢仔學校"},{"pid":"867bead1218cd7b71694b8ea35f39be6f2d9e454","tid":1748647,"uid":109117,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"a75c3466745c3703984d6f633533738e0d8bce2f","tid":1748647,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:57:01.000Z","msg":"有撚用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:59:58.000Z","msg":"有用過你呢句廢話"},{"pid":"ba0770301c0091bebf1be076333d4796794c174b","tid":1748647,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:00:38.000Z","msg":"多謝你地... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed93434209fa5539ff1de0f361858d865ea7b627","tid":1748647,"uid":49018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a75c3466745c3703984d6f633533738e0d8bce2f","tid":1748647,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:57:01.000Z","msg":"有撚用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:04:06.000Z","msg":"有用過你"},{"pid":"cb9fbdf3ea04c720270846dbedbad0902b7d3da1","tid":1748647,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a75c3466745c3703984d6f633533738e0d8bce2f","tid":1748647,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:57:01.000Z","msg":"有撚用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:06:37.000Z","msg":"你老母浮屍斬件做你宵夜"},{"pid":"a791214b4e56c3611310a41cb3e09dfad1405c09","tid":1748647,"uid":1110